@NODE "Introduction" "Introduction"
@TOC "MAIN"
Introduction:
-------------

 MIS is a program for copying and deleting icons. The thing
that makes this better then other similar programs is
that it's flexible and made by me :-)

 MultiIconSystem requires OS 2.0 or better.


@ENDNODE

