@NODE "Bugs, suggestions" "Bugs, suggestions"
@TOC "MAIN"
Buggs, suggestions:
----------------------

 If you find a bug in the program please write down what happened and
what computer, OS, special extension you have. And send it to me. And
I will try to fix it in the next version.
 
 If you have any good idea or comments, please write me a letter. If
I like it then I will try to fix it in the next update.

NOTE! If you have previously send a bugreport with bugs that don't
have been fixed, then please send it again, becourse I have lost
some bugreports and don't remember what the bugs was.



@ENDNODE

